TestIndirectGoalCycleThrows
/ Goals A → B → A (indirect cycle) trips ContainsGoal on the second Push of A. Wrap in error.handle so the test goal still completes.
- call CycleA, on error set %cycleCaught% = true
- assert %cycleCaught% is true, "indirect goal cycle A→B→A must trip ContainsGoal at the boundary crossing"
